      And I add "Accept" header equal to "application/json"
      And I send a "POST" request to "/locutions" with body:
    """
      {
          "name": "newLocution",
          "status": null,
          "encodedFile": {
              "fileSize": null,
              "mimeType": null,
              "baseName": null
          },
          "originalFile": {
              "fileSize": null,
              "mimeType": null,
              "baseName": null
          },
